              <img src="/assets/images/logo-512.png" alt="EJaytech Logo" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem; object-fit: contain;">
              <h4 class="fw-bold font-display text-dark mb-0">EJaytech Concepts</h4>
              <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Abuja Central Academic Command Centre Registry</p>
              <h5 class="fw-bold mt-2 text-primary font-display" style="text-decoration: underline;">OFFICIAL COURSE REGISTRATION SLIP</h5>
